title: How “Free Trade” Killed Our Middle Class - Now Below 50%
description:
Ari Rabin-Havt, -The Agenda/SiriusXM Progress/The Benghazi Hoax, joins Thom. Ever since Reagan radically transformed the American economy - the American middle class has been disappearing. It's gotten so bad that "middle class Americans" now make up less than half the country - according to a new report by Pew. But what does that mean for the country's economy - and can we reverse this trend?

For more information on the stories we've covered visit our websites at thomhartmann.com - freespeech.org - and RT.com. You can also watch tonight's show on Hulu - at Hulu.com/THE BIG PICTURE and over at The Big Picture YouTube page. And - be sure to check us out on Facebook and Twitter!
